<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zài zhòng rén qián yào jiān mò bì kǒu 迦南1031</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài zhòng rén qián yào jiān mò bì kǒu, zhǔ de líng zǎo bǎ wàn shì cān tòu.
 rén shì jiān shì shì fēi fēi, lù tú shàng qū zhé nán zǒu.
 wú rén zhù cháng jǔ shǒu, dào shén miàn qián duō xún qiú.
 yī shēng zhōng shí zài yǒu tài duō fēng yǔ, wéi yǒu zhǔ shì wǒ huàn nán zhōng de péng yǒu.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1031</hymn_number>
</song>